value: Resident on the coasts of Kamchatka; occurs on the Kurile Islands, Hokkaido and Sakhalin, but not breeding on these islands.

value: Oceanic, most numerous on near-shore waters and bays. Nests on masses of lichens in coniferous trees and (probably) on the ground.
